ZH: 我们在花园里玩捉迷藏。
EN: We play hide-and-seek in the garden.

ZH: 孩子们躲起来，玩起了捉迷藏的游戏。
EN: The children hid and started playing hide-and-seek.

ZH: 他们在公园里找不到最后一个人。
EN: They couldn't find the last person in the park.

ZH: 昨天晚上，我们家的小狗也一直在参与捉迷藏。
EN: Last night, our little dog was also involved in playing hide-and-seek.

ZH: 我再也找不到可以躲藏的地方了。
EN: I can't find any more hiding places.

ZH: 他一直躲在角落里。
EN: He has been hiding in the corner.

ZH: 谁能帮我找到我的钥匙？
EN: Who can help me find my keys?

ZH: 躲藏在树后面是最好的策略。
EN: Hiding behind a tree is the best strategy.

ZH: 我被她找到了，她真厉害！
EN: She found me, she's really good!

ZH: 来者不拒，你也可以一起加入我们玩捉迷藏。
EN: All are welcome, you can join us to play hide-and-seek.

ZH: 狐狸喜欢躲在草丛里。
EN: Foxes like to hide in the bushes.

ZH: 你得跑出去躲藏，否则他们会找到你的。
EN: You have to run and hide, otherwise they will find you.

ZH: 在城堡里找到所有的宝藏是一项挑战。
EN: Finding all the treasures in the castle is a challenge.

ZH: 小孩子们在家里玩捉迷藏，搞得满屋子都是笑声。
EN: The children play hide-and-seek at home, filling the whole house with laughter.

ZH: 他们把餐桌上的东西都藏得很好，我们找了很久也没找到。
EN: They hid the things on the dining table so well that we couldn't find them for a long time.

ZH: 躲起来的人必须保持安静。
EN: The person hiding must stay quiet.

ZH: 我告诉他不要躲在浴室里，可他还是没听我的。
EN: I told him not to hide in the bathroom, but he didn't listen to me.

ZH: 我们在密林中找寻着彼此。
EN: We search for each other in the dense forest.

ZH: 他找到了我藏在沙发下的地方。
EN: He found where I was hiding under the sofa.

ZH: 捉迷藏的时候，把手机关机是个好主意。
EN: It's a good idea to turn off your phone when playing hide-and-seek.
